edu.ucsd.cse110.group50.eventfinder

Class ServerLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucsd.cse110.group50.eventfinder.ServerLog

  • public class ServerLog
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to send logs to the server. Logs contain the time they were sent, a specified level, a tag (usually where it was sent from) and a message.
    Since:
    2016-11-20
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Thiago Marback
